{"ja378:0.1":"Jataka ","ja378:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","ja378:0.3":"Avariyavagga ","ja378:0.4":"3. Darimukhajataka ","ja378:1.1":"“Panko ca kama palipo ca kama, ","ja378:1.2":"Bhayanca metam timulam pavuttam; ","ja378:1.3":"Rajo ca dhumo ca maya pakasita, ","ja378:1.4":"Hitva tuvam pabbaja brahmadatta”. ","ja378:2.1":"“Gadhito ca ratto ca adhimucchito ca, ","ja378:2.2":"Kamesvaham brahmana bhimsarupam; ","ja378:2.3":"Tam nussahe jivikattho pahatum, ","ja378:2.4":"Kahami punnani anappakani”. ","ja378:3.1":"“Yo atthakamassa hitanukampino, ","ja378:3.2":"Ovajjamano na karoti sasanam; ","ja378:3.3":"Idameva seyyo iti mannamano, ","ja378:3.4":"Punappunam gabbhamupeti mando. ","ja378:4.1":"So ghorarupam nirayam upeti, ","ja378:4.2":"Subhasubham muttakarisapuram; ","ja378:4.3":"Satta sakaye na jahanti giddha, ","ja378:4.4":"Ye honti kamesu avitaraga”. ","ja378:5.1":"“Milhena litta ruhirena makkhita, ","ja378:5.2":"Semhena litta upanikkhamanti; ","ja378:5.3":"Yam yanhi kayena phusanti tavade, ","ja378:5.4":"Sabbam asatam dukhameva kevalam. ","ja378:6.1":"Disva vadami na hi annato savam, ","ja378:6.2":"Pubbenivasam bahukam sarami; ","ja378:6.3":"Citrahi gathahi subhasitahi, ","ja378:6.4":"Darimukho nijjhapayi sumedhan”ti. ","ja378:7.1":"Darimukhajatakam tatiyam. "}